The '''''Edict''''' was one of the two [[Gamma-class assault shuttle/Legends|''Gamma''-class assault shuttles]] carried aboard the [[Imperial I-class Star Destroyer/Legends|''Imperial I''-class Star Destroyer]] ''[[Gorgon]]''. It was used by [[Admiral/Legends|Admiral]] [[Natasi Daala|Daala]] in [[11 ABY/Legends|11 ABY]].

